	iteration or not

	* premia_wrap.c : is_with_iter method added

30-11-08 Jérôme Lelong  <jerome.lelong@ensta.fr>

	* set_option corrected to prevent scripts to pick up an option
	which is uncomptatible with the model.
	

25-11-08 Jérôme Lelong  <jerome.lelong@ensta.fr>

	* set_asset uses named argument "str" instead of "asset"

	* set_{model,option,method} accept a named argument "str" in
	addition to the already existing integer arguments.


29-10-08 Jérôme Lelong  <jerome.lelong@ensta.fr>

	* Method get_method_results[] returns an empty list if the compute
	method has not been called.


27-10-08 Jérôme Lelong  <jerome.lelong@ensta.fr>

	* Field Meth.Res are now saved to file together with the object
	and reloaded when needed.

