	* A textview widget has been added to the main window to diplay
	the results of a single computation.


17-10-08 Jérôme Lelong  <jerome.lelong@ensta.fr>

	* New field added to a PremiaModel object to store the return of
	the compute methods and display the right error message when
	needed.
  

